 The virus was hit by the energon. It didnt have any defense. It came close 
to destruction. Famine was signaled. He looked down and was astonished. 
 "Well.... I guess I will have to use the back up." He pressed the button on 
his arm. Suddenly the virus glowed. Though not much was left it had adapted 
to survive and at least 25% was left. It's cell chemicals where combined. The 
reaction started. It started the process. Soon... it would explode. The clock 
ticked. Hell Beast would not be able to feel this happening for how small the 
virus had diminished. It would only have the explosive capability to take out 
hell beast. Unlike noraml when it would take out a mile beyond. The spark was 
tricked and the explosion would ahppen in three seconds.... Famine looked at 
his watch...
 3, 
 2, 
 1,
 boom. The virus self destructed.
